ericj@@oshibana:~&gt; <strong>export CVSROOT=anoncvs@@anoncvs.usa.openbsd.org:/cvs</strong>
ericj@@oshibana:~&gt; <strong>cvs get src</strong>
d999 1
a999 1
As of OpenBSD 2.6, you need to use /dev/cuaXX for connections initiated
