<li><a href= "faq8.html#8.19">8.19 - I'm having problems with my NIC's being detected in OpenBSD 2.8.</a>
d1171 1
a1171 1
<h2>8.19 - I'm having problems with my NIC's being detected in OpenBSD 2.8.</h2>
d1174 1
a1174 1
There exists a condition in OpenBSD 2.8 where some machines might not detect NIC's properly, or might freeze while detecting multiple NIC's in one machine. This is the fault of PCIBIOS, and involves a simple workaround to make work properly.
d1218 1
a1218 1
